title: Feast of Flesh (The Deadly Organ)
description:
FEAST OF FLESH (a.k.a. The Deadly Organ)
Made in Argentina under the title "Placer sangriento"

Something Weird Video
MPEG-4 encoded from DVD-R

Dubbed in English for the American grindhouse market

Police hunt for a mysterious person who is abducting girls at a seaside resort, then enslaving them with heroin, sex and "wild music."  Who's responsible? Why? Who's next? Is anyone safe?

Meet "The Fiend Behind the Mask!"

Some pretty women, lame police humor, and a bizarre concept. Worth a look, but then see THE CURIOUS DR. HUMPP which takes this concept to the next level.

Torrent includes feature in letterbox format and American trailer.
